  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Path of Meditation:</strong> 7th level</em></p>\n<p>Once per long rest, you can cast the <em>battle meditation</em> force power at its base level without expending force points. While concentrating on <em>battle meditation</em>, at the start of each of your turns, the power's die increases by one step (from [[/r d4]] to [[/r d6]], [[/r d6]] to [[/r d8]], [[/r d8]] to [[/r d10]], or [[/r d10]] to [[/r d12]]).</p>\n<p>Additionally, whenever you make a Constitution saving throw to maintain concentration on a force power, you can treat a [[/r d20]] roll of 9 or lower as a 10.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
